Class RouteMapComponent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.atakmap.android.maps.AbstractMapComponent
      • com.atakmap.android.widgets.AbstractWidgetMapComponent
        • com.atakmap.android.routes.RouteMapComponent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MapComponent, CotServiceRemote.ConnectionListener

    public class RouteMapComponent
extends AbstractWidgetMapComponent
implements CotServiceRemote.ConnectionListener
    Provides for all of the routing capability within the architecture. The core capability is simple, but allows for augmentation to support more capabilities. For a full turn by turn example, please see the vns plugin.
